stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    state "Data Assembly" as DataAssembly
    state "FHIR Mapping" as FHIRMapping
    state "Validation Check" as ValidationCheck
    state "Transmission" as Transmission
    [*] --> DataAssembly: Scheduled export starts
    DataAssembly --> FHIRMapping: System prepares standardized records
    FHIRMapping --> ValidationCheck: Bundle is created
    ValidationCheck --> Transmission: Bundle passes validation
    ValidationCheck --> Error: Bundle fails schema validation
    Transmission --> Complete: External endpoint accepts the data
    Transmission --> Error: Transport or authentication error occurs
    Complete --> [*]: Export completes
    Error --> [*]: Error is logged
